freetext.HEALTHCARE_VISITS_OTHER: I took Advil a few times to help with my fever and body aches Friday night and Saturday. Advil is a known irritant to my stomach, so the Advil caused me to have a gastritis flare (which I have had before- I do not believe related to my vaccine). I sought out care at the ER for this.

freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: Yesterday I had a bad taste in my mouth.
